data.description: Welcome to this stunning townhouse located in the heart of Frederick, MD, offering convenience and modern living at its finest. Built in 2015, this impeccably maintained townhouse boasts 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths, providing ample space for comfortable living. Experience the ultimate in walkability as you stroll to nearby restaurants, a gym, and a grocery store, ensuring convenience at your doorstep. Commute with ease with close proximity to major commuter routes, making travel a breeze for work or leisure. Step inside to discover brand new carpeting throughout and freshly painted walls, showcasing a move-in ready home updated in February 2024. Enjoy the elegance of hardwood floors, the sleekness of stainless steel appliances, and the sophistication of granite countertops in the kitchen. Entertain with style in the spacious living areas, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply relaxing with loved ones. Retreat to the privacy of the bedrooms, including a luxurious master suite, offering comfort and tranquility after a busy day. Embrace the convenience of modern living while savoring the charm of the surrounding neighborhood, creating the perfect balance of lifestyle and comfort. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful townhouse your new home sweet home in Frederick, MD.
